      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. STEELY DAWN was narrowly beaten last time, jumping from this same box when a 0.8 lengths second in a Grade 5 over 411m at Casino. Has the ability and looks hard to top. 1. NOIR RIPPLE scored well last start as odds-on favourite by one length at this track in a handy 20.10 beating Joker Bonus. Nicely placed here on the inside and goes well over this trip. Has never been out of the placings from three starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. 6. MOST DETERMINED is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 20.31 beating Tyketto. Expected to measure up again. 5. WILGUNYA PRINCE is worth consideration.\",\"runners\":[2,1,6,5],\"exclusive\":false}",
